>9</span>月以来第三次出现负值，并创下<span>2013</span>年<span>2</span>月以来最低水平。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	美国劳工部报告：<span>12</span>月<span>12</span>日当周美国申领失业救济人数为<span>27.1</span>万人，低于预期的<span>27.5</span>万人<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\">\r\n	<b>2.&nbsp;&nbsp; </b><b>言论<span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	欧洲央行管委诺沃特尼：尽管速度较慢，<span>QE</span>仍将有助于通胀回归目标水平。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	委内瑞拉总统马杜罗：美联储加息不利于油价。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	富国<span><a href=\"http://news.fx678.com/C/20151218/201512180633191854.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">证券</a></span>汇市<span><a href=\"http://t.fx678.com/strategy/index.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">策略</a></span>师<span>Eric&nbsp;Viloria</span>表示，“美联储开始逐步升息，而包括<span><a href=\"http://news.fx678.com/C/20151218/201512180633191854.shtml\" target=\"_blank\"><span>欧洲</span></a><a href=\"http://news.fx678.com/news/bank/index.shtml\" target=\"_blank\"><span>央行</span></a></span>和<span><a href=\"http://news.fx678.com/news/keywords/boj.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">日本央行</a></span>在内的其他央行还在维持宽松<span><a href=\"http://news.fx678.com/news/currency/index.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">货币</a></span>政策，这在一段时间内对美元有支撑作用。”<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	<b>3. </b><b>产油国动态<span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	据外媒：世界银行批准向伊拉克提供<span>12</span>亿美元的紧急贷款以应对原油行业和国家安全受到的冲击。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	埃克森美孚据称将关闭位于比利时的安特卫普炼油厂，该炼油厂原油产量为<span>32</span>万桶<span>/</span>日，因此前<span>12</span>月<span>12</span>日当地工会与埃克森美孚的薪资谈判失败将引发工人罢工。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	尼日利亚石油部长：预计<span>2016</span>年石油产量为<span>240</span>万桶<span>/</span>日。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp;</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	<strong>三， 综合评述<span></span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;text-align:justify;\">\r\n	美国费城联储制造业录得负值，是过去四个月中第三次告负，若扩散至美国全国的制造业行业，制造业疲软，石油需求不济。美加息后，受益最大的是美元，从<span>98</span>涨至<span>99</span>，以美元标价的原油价格承压下行，市场还正受到美国能源信息署<span>EIA</span>周三原油库存报告所带来之“余震”的影响。全球指标布伦特原油收位离<span>2004</span>年低位不远。油价还能在<span>11</span>年低位之上撑多久的不确定性使一些市场人士作壁上观。石油输出国组织<span>(</span><span><a href=\"http://news.fx678.com/news/keywords/opec.shtml\" target=\"_blank\">OPEC</a></span>)预计， <span>2016</span>年油价明显上涨的可能性不大， 这增加了油市的利空人气。综合看，石油需求不济，而产能或将进一步扩大，美加息后美指再次走强，油价承压下行。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm;\">\r\n	<b>四， 今日关注数据<span></span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<table class=\"MsoTableLightShadingAccent1\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"565\" style=\"width:423.6pt;border:none;\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border:solid #4F81BD 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">时间<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"94\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border:solid #4F81BD 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">国家地区<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"255\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border:solid #4F81BD 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">指标<span></span></span> \r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"76\" valign=\"top\" style=\"border:solid #4F81BD 1.0pt;\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-s